<HEADLINE>
WE'LL SURVIVE IMPEACHMENT  
 (ADV: THIS EDITORIAL APPEARED IN THE DEC. 18 ARIZONA REPUBLIC)  
 (FOR USE BY N.Y. TIMES NEWS SERVICE CLIENTS) 
</HEADLINE>
   c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
