stocking with two decorating pieces by Martha Stewart, two
historical pieces _ about the evolution of Christmas customs and
about America's first Christmas card, a software gift list for
children, a how-to article on scrapbooking and an essay by a Jewish
woman who feels ``assaulted'' by Christmas.
