 Friday, Dec. 18, 1998    
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file these stories for
Saturday and Sunday. If you have questions, please call Susie McBee
or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920.
</P>
