recent events on Capitol Hill, might be grist for the tabloids, or
worse. But, besides including sex, it describes topics expressed by
such literary forms such as poetry and short stories express but
not by other forms of modern entertainment. Tauzin says this isn't
an accident. For him, poetry is like ``listening to music in stereo
