   VIRGIN ISLANDS -- GREEN. Today's vote on impeaching President
Clinton is more an attempt by Republicans to get rid of a leader
they don't like than to hold him accountable for having an affair,
V.I. Delegate to Congress Donna Christian-Green told her House
colleagues Friday. Williams
</P>
<P>
   WISCONSIN -- IMPEACHMENT. Wisconsin lawmakers' remarks during
the impeachment debate. Hurt
</P>
<P>
   -30-
