most of the sport-utilities really are just trucks underneath _ no
matter how fancy they are. That leaves a market for a luxury
station wagon, hence Mercedes' introduction last year of its latest
high-end wagon, the E320. By G. CHAMBERS WILLIAMS III. Story will
