<P>
   FOOTBALL
</P>
<P>
   PROS
</P>
<P>
   FBN-REEVES _ Tearful Falcons coach Dan Reeves holds an emotional
news conference prior to his released from Piedmont Hospital after
heart surgery. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 15. WITH
PHOTO.
</P>
