or photos please call 212 556-4204 or -1927.
</P>
<P>
   All stories will bear the BOS designator.
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   IRAQ-SANCTIONS (Baghdad) _ Saddam says on TV he will not
compromise. It is now clear that UNSCOM is history unless sanctions
are lifted. By Charles M. Sennott. 1500 words.
</P>
