politics of smear and slash-and-burn must end!'' For the briefest
moment in a day of bear-pit partisanship, Republicans and Democrats
cheered as one. The scene. By Francis X. Clines.
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-CLINTON (Washington) _ A day story on the president. By
James Bennet. (900 words)
</P>
