<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-18 19:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7610 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-IRAQ-RUSSIA-BOS &LR;      12-18 1271
