<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-18 19:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7616 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-IRAQ-PENTAGON-BOS &LR;      12-18 1192
