<DOCNO> NYT19981218.0356 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-18 20:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7713 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STOLEN-ART-BOS &LR;      12-18 0916
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-STOLEN-ART-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
JEWISH GROUP OBJECTS TO LABEL ON PAINTING 
</HEADLINE>
  
