<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-18 20:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7783 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MINDBOGGLING-REI-SEAT     12-18 1240
