   COMBAT-WOMEN (Undated) _ For the first time, U.S. female
military aviators are flying combat missions as Operation Desert
Fox continues against Iraq.
</P>
<P>
   By Ed Offley. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   ARMED-RANGERS (Olympia, Wash.) _ Washington State Parks rangers
will be armed, the state Parks and Recreation Commission decides
after hearing emotional pleas from rangers who say it's pretty darn
dangerous out there.
</P>
<P>
   By Tom Shapley. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   SMITH-WORKPLACE-COLUMN (Undated) If holiday spending has put you
into a panic or a frenzy, it's not too late to do something about
it. Just stop.
</P>
<P>
   By Carol Smith. (Story will move in the ``f'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   BOEING-GOLFER (Seattle) _ Pro Golfer Greg Norman, whose
high-profile order for Boeing's first business jet was used not
only to launch the new business jet program but to promote it in
the company's advertising, has cancelled his order.
</P>
<P>
   By Bruce Ramsey. (Story will move in the ``f'' category.)
