   (NYT24) ABOARD USS ENTERPRISE -- Dec. 18, 1998 -- IRAQ-U.S.-3,
12-18 -- An array of bombs and missiles crowds the hangar bay of
the USS Enterprise on Friday as the aircraft carrier cruises the
Persian Gulf. The weaponry is transported up to the flight deck
where it is attached to fighters and bombers taking part in
Operation Desert Fox. (William R. Crosby/New York Times Photo)
</P>
