IRAQ-U.S.-2, 12-18 -- A pilot suits up for a mission in support of
Operation Desert Fox on Friday aboard the USS Enterprise. The
aircraft carrier is leading an armada of warships in the Persian
Gulf as part of military strikes against Iraq. (Jason D. Malcom/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT21) SOUTHAMPTON, N.Y. -- Dec. 18, 1998 -- ADV. FOR SUN.,
DEC. 20 -- PARTY-PLANNERS-2, 12-18 -- Place settings pairing
Barcarole roses and figs with the client's collection of Vermeil
palm-tree candlesticks as prepared by Susan Miller Smith. The place
settings were part of Ms. Smith's party arrangements made for a
fund-raiser in August for the Watermill Center. (James Estrin/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
