-- FBN-YOGA, 12-18 -- Danny Poole helps Shannon Sharpe, the Denver
Broncos' tight end, with a pre-game posture. Poole, who looks a
decade younger than his 49 years, is no saffron-robed yogi. ``Most
jocks I see don't know anything about yoga,'' says Poole. ``They
think it's some guy chanting with his leg behind his neck.''
(Frances Roberts/New York Times Photo) *LITE
