   (NYT1) ABOARD THE USS ENTERPRISE -- Dec. 18, 1998 --
IRAQ-U.S.-1, 12-18 -- A trail of light is left by an F/A-18 Hornet
as it takes off from the flight deck of the USS Enterprise after
being waved clear by the catapault officer on Thursday. The
aircraft carrier, sailing in the Persian Gulf, is leading an armada
of warships as part of Operation Desert Fox. (Timothy S. Smith/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
