<HEADLINE>
PARIS METRO TO SMELL SWEETER  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Travel Editors)   (This 350-word ``separate buy'' article is from The Independent
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from New York Times
