<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-18 23:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8158 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBN-MODESTI-COLUMN-LA     12-18 0932
